snippet.title: Ghislaine Maxwell Doesn't Like Her Life in Jail: What she now wants a judge to do?
snippet.description:
#GhislaineMaxwell doesn't like her life in jail. The accused sex trafficker wants to join "gen pop" and says the constant observations, body searches, and suicide clothes are unfair. What do you think?
